Contact : Pierre Navaro

Simple advection tests with Backward Semi Lagrangian.

We want to test boundary conditions for :
 - cubic spline 1D
 - cubic spline 2D
 - arbitrary spline 1D
 - arbitrary spline 2D

Directory structure
===================
   advection_1d1d_cubic_splines -- executable
   README                       -- info (this file)
   run/                         -- output directory

HOWTO
=====
0. Create output directory if missing, and move into it
     $ mkdir run
     $ cd run

1. Run parallel simulation within directory
     $ mpirun -np 4 ../bin/advection_1d1d_cubic_splines 

2. Run gnuplot script generated at runtime
     $ gnuplot --persist f_parallel.gnu


